{"tid":2249812,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"40歲陳冠希光頭look被嘲似小丸子爺爺！回顧入行20年外型進化史！","createTime":"2020-10-19T14:49:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T05:52:11.000Z","uid":147522,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f2d7ffa81075a3fc193a3bb80ce7fd9de9f15710","tid":2249812,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T14:49:09.000Z","msg":"40歲嘅陳冠希（Edison）出道20年，係唔少人心目中嘅「男神」，又創立品牌成「潮人」。近年外貌經常成為話題，指佢靚仔樣不再，佢最近造型更被恥笑似小丸子爺爺！<br />\n<br />\n陳冠希（Edison）今年40歲，2000年出道憑混血靚仔樣成為唔少女性心目中嘅「男神」，參演過唔少電影。<br />\n<br />\n淡出娛樂圈後佢創立個人品牌，獲封潮人。不過近年佢常被指外貌崩壞，靚仔樣不再，最新造型更成為話題，被嘲似小丸子爺爺。<br />\n<br />\n其實Edison嘅外貌一向備受關注，佢2000年出道時簡直驚為天人，不論男女都被佢外貌迷倒，一齊嚟睇佢出道20年外貌進化史：<br />\n<br />\n《特警新人類2》<br />\n<br />\n演「Edison」一角，紅色頭髮同佢壞壞嘅氣質好夾。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/37EXiLC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F37EXiLC.jpg&h=20f8d8e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《無間道》<br />\n<br />\n飾演年青時嘅劉德華，著制服非常型仔。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BN0jw5H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBN0jw5H.jpg&h=9e1b2003&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《新紮師兄》<br />\n<br />\n仍然靚仔，同謝霆鋒合作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvZDND6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvZDND6.jpg&h=55b24326&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《頭文字D》<br />\n<br />\n當年25歲，食煙都咁型。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ythh3cu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYthh3cu.jpg&h=607de032&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《金雞SSS》<br />\n<br />\n造型搞笑，但外型仍睇得出當年嘅面貌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eXaC3cz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeXaC3cz.jpg&h=29aee70b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾經有一張圖非常流行，就係陳冠希同一位阿伯「換臉」照，而Edison不論著白背心，定係裇衫都咁型，完美演繹「你的樣子如何」、「時尚嘅完成係臉」。<br />\n<br />\n不過早喺兩個月前，Edison post出一家三口嘅合照，佢笑到現晒魚尾紋，不過佢已近40歲，其實都好正常。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V6zcR5Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV6zcR5Y.jpg&h=b98ea4a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而曾經係「你的樣子如何」代言人嘅Edison以往就算著白背心都咁型，依家新造型就似水喉工、小丸子爺爺，昔日男神樣不再，令人不勝唏噓。"},{"pid":"56c5a52f7b0f2367161c70ea04b491032ed95ef4","tid":2249812,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T14:50:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V6zcR5Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV6zcR5Y.jpg&h=b98ea4a8&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n3個男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c2aef4ffb1b478696fcccfc029b79a15318203","tid":2249812,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56c5a52f7b0f2367161c70ea04b491032ed95ef4","tid":2249812,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T14:50:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V6zcR5Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV6zcR5Y.jpg&h=b98ea4a8&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n3個男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T14:51:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b44e22b217ab0866fea922c1a4e89bd14f47e28d","tid":2249812,"uid":192078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56c5a52f7b0f2367161c70ea04b491032ed95ef4","tid":2249812,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T14:50:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V6zcR5Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV6zcR5Y.jpg&h=b98ea4a8&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n3個男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" clas